  "texts": [
    "For the sake of the argument, I will assume some shared intuitions on what is the morally right choice in a range of decision-making situations.",
    "Insofar as these shared intuitions are absent, machine ethics, of a kind that is democratically legitimate, will of course become more problematic.",
    "But the goal of the current paper is to examine obstacles for machine ethics even if significant moral agreement can be assumed.",
    "Second, we need to explicate the term 'sufficient reliability'.",
    "On the basis of what criteria would we say that a system reliably behaves morally?"
  ],
